{"title": "Stay put or go in? Analysts\u2019 take for S\u2019pore investors in China\u2019s beaten-down equity markets", "tags": "business", "timestamp": "2024-02-08", "content": "SINGAPORE \u2013 Chinese markets have extended gains for the fourth straight session on Feb 8 ahead of the week-long Spring Festival break.\nThe CSI 300 Index, the blue-chip benchmark for the Shanghai and Shenzhen exchanges, has risen 4.5 per cent over the past four days but remains near a five-year low following three years of market correction."}